dcterms:description: DBLP is a monthly updated citation network dataset. It contains three kinds of node types: paper (P), author (A), and conference (C). The dataset is used to detect communities such as Information Retrieval, Data Base, and Machine Learning.
dcterms:title: DBLP

dcterms:description: IMDB is a widely adopted dataset for heterogeneous graph analysis. It consists of information about directors, actors, and movie release dates. The dataset is used to detect communities such as Action, Adventure, Comedy, Crime, and Drama.
dcterms:title: IMDB
